<p dir="auto">Note that it is <em>critical</em> that you include <code>../web-component-tester/browser.js</code>
in your test suites. <code>browser.js</code> contains all of WCT's client logic (and loads
bundled libraries like mocha and chai). You can also load it from the absolute URL <code>/components/web-component-tester/browser.js</code>.</p>
