</tr>
<tr>
<td>ignoredTests</td>
<td>Array (optional)</td>
<td>Tests to ignore. <br>Test names are found <a href="https://github.com/GoogleChrome/accessibility-developer-tools/blob/master/dist/js/axs_testing.js">here</a> as calls to axs.AuditRules.addRule()</td>
